                'B) RSQ is a centralized state-wide service; transport planning is influenced by geographical distance (plane vs. helicopter range), geographical terrain, landing sites, weather, and time of day.',
                "C) RSQ is an inpatient specialty team; transport is determined by the hospital's flat hierarchy.",
