                'A) It indicates a high risk of systemic local anesthetic toxicity.',
                'B) It suggests the patient will have a low tolerance to post-operative pain.',
                'C) Prior head and neck surgeries can significantly alter airway anatomy due to previous flaps, increasing the risk of a difficult airway.',
